what did you want
to talk to me about?

1077
01:24:10.079 --> 01:24:12.944
Have you thought about getting
into the music business?

1078
01:24:13.082 --> 01:24:16.396
- Crossover-type thing?
- I don't follow you.

1079
01:24:17.259 --> 01:24:19.088
Well. I'm about to take

1080
01:24:19.226 --> 01:24:20.848
- my boys on a world tour.
- Hmm.

1081
01:24:20.986 --> 01:24:22.619
You know. we're gonna start
with North America.

1082
01:24:22.643 --> 01:24:24.128
- You know. stadiums only.
- Hmm.

1083
01:24:24.266 --> 01:24:26.095
You know. the biggest.

1084
01:24:26.233 --> 01:24:28.477
It's time to show the world
that the Jacksons are back.

1085
01:24:28.615 --> 01:24:30.651
- Right on. Okay.
- And bigger than ever.

1086
01:24:30.789 --> 01:24:32.149
You've seen them sales
on Thriller.

1087
01:24:32.239 --> 01:24:33.620
- Huh?
- Mm-hmm.

1088
01:24:33.758 --> 01:24:34.942
People are gonna be
climbing the walls.

1089
01:24:38.107 --> 01:24:40.144
Is Michael gonna be there?

1090
01:24:44.148 --> 01:24:45.804
Of course Michael's
gonna be there.

1091
01:24:45.942 --> 01:24:47.772
Hmm. That's good to hear.

1092
01:24:48.635 --> 01:24:50.740
Now. what's in it for me?

1093
01:24:53.295 --> 01:24:54.848
I've been watching you. Don.

1094
01:24:54.986 --> 01:24:56.815
- I watch you like a hawk.
- Hmm.

1095
01:24:56.953 --> 01:24:59.335
I love the way
you promote your fighters.

1096
01:24:59.473 --> 01:25:01.337
- Uh-huh.
- You're the king of marketing.

1097
01:25:01.475 --> 01:25:04.064
You know. I just. uh.
I think that you and I.

1098
01:25:04.202 --> 01:25:06.308
if we came together.
we could. uh...

1099
01:25:07.550 --> 01:25:09.069
we could form
a good partnership.

1100
01:25:09.207 --> 01:25:10.588
Me and you?

1101
01:25:10.726 --> 01:25:12.555
